    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378620/extras/5828afdd4d30c69db05f61c202c9be14.poster.avif?t=1770196035\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378620/extras/5828afdd4d30c69db05f61c202c9be14.webm?t=1770196035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>《时空叛客》设定于一个赛博朋克的世界中，故事的主角70号特工需要面对因时空错乱而导致的各种异常现象。在一个又一个奇妙而错乱的时空中穿行，与各种克隆体敌人战斗，运用特工擅长的战斗技巧，以及奇妙的特工装备，尽全力击溃所有的敌人，拯救世界于危机之中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378620/extras/558e816f78d2b26a4087d17cf7ab26e2.poster.avif?t=1770196035\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378620/extras/558e816f78d2b26a4087d17cf7ab26e2.webm?t=1770196035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378620/extras/558e816f78d2b26a4087d17cf7ab26e2.mp4?t=1770196035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>运用近战武器及枪械的独特连击动作击溃所有敌人。<br></li><li>神奇的特工装备，让你巧妙应对敌人攻击。<br></li><li>用特技般的动作摆脱敌人及各种机关陷阱的威胁。<br></li><li>收集资源道具，升级你的特工装备及技能。<br></li><li>随着故事情节的发展，一步步地揭露异变的真相，拯救世界……或是让世界彻底毁灭。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378620/extras/0120915f17073ae8e1853fdcf662b67d.poster.avif?t=1770196035\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378620/extras/0120915f17073ae8e1853fdcf662b67d.webm?t=1770196035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378620/extras/0120915f17073ae8e1853fdcf662b67d.mp4?t=1770196035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>穿梭于赛博朋克的时空之中，跟随着80年代的合成波音乐，体验一场复古且新颖的冒险。结识众多令人难忘的角色、挑战独特的异常BOSS、感受这充满曲折的故事，希望各位能享受这段奇妙的旅程。",
